{"tid":1854241,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"子瑜深U短裙看光「美胸鎖骨、辣腿根」網怒：沒誠意","createTime":"2020-01-31T11:27:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-31T17:21:32.000Z","uid":74065,"like":2,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"914f50345bf214119fd1ac292076680fa1d73d9a","tid":1854241,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T11:27:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://images.chinatimes.com/newsphoto/2020-01-31/900/20200131001789.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.chinatimes.com%2Fnewsphoto%2F2020-01-31%2F900%2F20200131001789.jpg&h=97b78908&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n南韓一年一度的音樂盛會「第29屆首爾歌謠大賞」於30號晚間盛大展開，大勢女團TWICE不但榮獲大獎並擔任表演嘉賓，在紅毯上的穿搭一樣成為眾人矚目的焦點。<br />\n<br />\n27日結束假期返回韓國的台灣成員子瑜，雖受到疫情的影響全程戴著口罩依然擋不住巨星風采，在機場便受到大批粉絲包圍。而在30日的頒獎典禮紅毯上她以一襲深U超激短裙與團員們一同露出白皙長腿，領口低胸設計更讓她的事業線若隱若現，不過這樣的穿搭卻遭到眼尖的網友發現，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">其實早已在日本NHK新年節目《紅白歌合戰》中亮相過，讓不少粉絲替她們抱不平，認為經紀公司太沒有誠意，再次引發話題。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n子瑜表情撩人超忘我！扯掉長裙「小褲全都露」<br />\n子瑜為舒華慶生合影！「雙頰消風」驚人對比網心疼<br />\n子瑜中空上衣熱舞！一抬手「炸出肋骨、大腿線條」網暴動"},{"pid":"9244e212bae4562382604662c8f2c3f4c43794bf","tid":1854241,"uid":34489,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T11:31:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/AG8z7Y1.jpg?1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FAG8z7Y1.jpg%3F1&h=9fa0e698&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5b773b3dd6aa9874496ec17e300955fd302ddf78","tid":1854241,"uid":166062,"like":8,"dislike":4,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T11:33:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/opuRZsq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FopuRZsq.png&h=d3471103&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7a65d1c095824cb9ab0c9d45b0ebb7a79c55de07","tid":1854241,"uid":221478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T11:35:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"386564004a8908da9fbb57909aef72d